WhereIsHe
========

A software for tracking where your coworkers/friends are. This project is still far from complete.

Basic features:
* Allows setting up places where you can be
* You can share places with groups
* Allows creating a view which contains all the places and people in a group(useful for a big screen like tv)

Possible ways to track:
* Web ui for marking where you are
* Phone app for reading GPS coordinates or wlans
* Login/Logout of computer
* Facebook/Foursquares integration?

Technologies:
* REST based API with Node.js and Express
* Data stored in MongoDB
* UI made with static html / javascript


